<h1 id="toc4"><span>不使用动画格式制作动画</span></h1>
<div class="scp-image-block" style="width:300px;">
<p><iframe src="http://scpsandbox-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/dr-devan/SCP-895.html" align="" frameborder="0" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="width:300px; height:220px;"></iframe></p>
<div class="scp-image-caption" style="width:300px;">
<p>一个著名的例子</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="scp-image-block" style="width:300px;">
<p><iframe src="http://scp-jp-sandbox2.wdfiles.com/local--files/nanimono-demonai/RedMars.html" align="" frameborder="0" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="width:300px; height:300px;"></iframe></p>
