<p>Code:4</p>
</div>
<br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[div&#32;class=&quot;DummyForumTitle&quot;]]～[[/div]]</span>之间的“无序列表”（即“<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">*&#32;list</span>”）会变成帖子的类别。
<p><strong>摘要：</strong>摘要放在帖子标题下方，简要概述帖子的用途。</p>
<div class="dummyDescription">
<div class="DummyStatistics">开始由: <span class="printuser avatarhover"><img src="http://scp-jp-sandbox2.wdfiles.com/local--files/inc%3Aaddspecialcss/dummyaccount3.png" class="small" alt="dummyaccount3.png" /><span class="fake-link">QuestionMan</span></span><br />
日期: 2 Apr 2017&#160;12:08<br />
文章数: 3<br />
<span class="rss-icon"><img src="http://www.wikidot.com/common--theme/base/images/feed/feed-icon-14x14.png" class="" alt="feed-icon-14x14.png" /></span>RSS: <span class="fake-link">新文章</span></div>
<div class="dummySummaySentence" style="display:block">
<p>我想写一篇关于讨论区的meta文章！</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="dummyOptions">
