</div>
<p>语法如下：</p>
<blockquote>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[include&#32;:scpsandboxcn:inc:pseudosummary&#32;|</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">URL=http://scp-jp-sandbox2.wdfiles.com/local--files/inc%3Aaddspecialcss/dummyaccount3.png|</span><br />
NAME=QuestionMan |<br />
DATE=26 Jan 2017&#160;12:08|<br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">POST=3|</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">SUMMARY&#32;=</span> <strong>block</strong><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">]]</span><br />
我想写一篇关于讨论区的meta文章！<br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[include&#32;:scpsandboxcn:inc:pseudosummary-end]]</span></p>
</blockquote>
<div style="text-align:center;font-weight:bold;">
<p>Code:5</p>
</div>
<br />
这里URL等各种设置项，其功能说明如下：
<table class="wiki-content-table" style="width:100%">
<tr>
<th style="width:9em;">项目</th>
<th>设置内容</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="width:9em;">URL</td>
<td>用户头像图片的URL地址</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="width:9em;">NAME</td>
<td>讨论发起人用户名</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="width:9em;">DATE</td>
<td>帖子创建日期</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="width:9em;">POST</td>
<td>文章总数</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="width:9em;">SUMMARY</td>
<td><strong>※详见下文</strong></td>
</tr>
</table>
<div style="text-align:center;font-weight:bold;">
<p>Explain:1</p>
</div>
<br />
有关SUMMARY的设置，举例说明：
<div class="dummyDescription">
<div class="DummyStatistics">开始由: <span class="printuser avatarhover"><img src="http://scp-jp-sandbox2.wdfiles.com/local--files/inc%3Aaddspecialcss/dummyaccount3.png" class="small" alt="dummyaccount3.png" /><span class="fake-link">QuestionMan</span></span><br />
日期: 2 Apr 2017&#160;12:08<br />
文章数: 3<br />
<span class="rss-icon"><img src="http://www.wikidot.com/common--theme/base/images/feed/feed-icon-14x14.png" class="" alt="feed-icon-14x14.png" /></span>RSS: <span class="fake-link">新文章</span></div>
<div class="dummySummaySentence" style="display:none"></div>
</div>
<div class="dummyOptions">
<p><span class="fake-link">全部展开</span> <span class="fake-link">全部收合</span> <span class="fake-link">更多选项</span></p>
</div>
<p>如果帖子没有摘要，同时也要将“摘要:”隐藏，将SUMMARY设置成none。</p>
<blockquote>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[include&#32;:scpsandboxcn:inc:pseudosummary&#32;|</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">URL=http://scp-jp-sandbox2.wdfiles.com/local--files/inc%3Aaddspecialcss/dummyaccount3.png|</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">NAME=QuestionMan&#32;|</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">DATE=2&#32;Apr&#32;2017&#32;12:08|</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">POST=3|</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">SUMMARY=</span><strong>none</strong><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">]]</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[include&#32;:scpsandboxcn:inc:pseudosummary-end]]</span></p>
</blockquote>
